These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea
There 2 different types of food: broccoli, spinach
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: dahlia, zinnia
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, sports
1. the person watching action movies is not to the right of the person eating spinach##8
2. the person eating spinach is somewhere to the left of the person who growsdahlia##5
3. the person drinking coffee is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Beverage      | tea     | coffee      |
| Food          | spinach | broccoli    |
| Flower         | zinnia   | dahlia |
| Movie-Genre   | action  | sports      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea
The people have 2 different hobbies: filmmaking, woodworking
There are 2 different favourite colors: purple, light-blue
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, snowmobile
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the left of the person who likes purple##5
3. the person who likes light-blue is not to the right of the person who likes purple##8
4. the person driving the boat is not the person who's hobby is woodworking##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Beverage    | almond-milk        | iced-tea    |
| Hobby       | filmmaking         | woodworking |
| Color         | light-blue | purple   |
| Transport   | boat               | snowmobile  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: epic, thriller
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, metal
There are 2 different nationalities: australian, japanese
The people have 2 different hobbies: sudoku, gardening
1. the australian is in an odd position##4
2. the japanese is not to the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##8
3. the fan of folk is somewhere to the left of the person watching thriller movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic       | thriller |
| Music-Genre   | folk       | metal    |
| Nationality   | australian | japanese |
| Hobby           | sudoku        | gardening   |

