2. the mexican is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is not the person watching drama movies##6
4. the person watching drama movies is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in may##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
